OL,5, Hollywood actor Johnny Depp has made a 
OL,6, terminally ill boy's "dreams come true"
OL,7, by calling him on video and surprising 
OL,8, him with a PlayStation 5 for Christmas.
OL,10,FThe star also delighted Pirates of the 
OL,11,FCaribbean fan Kori, 11, by reprising   
OL,12,Fthe role of Captain Jack Sparrow for   
OL,13,Fhim in the 20-minute video call.       
OL,15,FKori has undergone two unsuccessful    
OL,16,Fheart transplants and his family say   
OL,17,Fthey do not know how long he will live.
OL,19,FHis mum Pixi said he was "overwhelmed" 
OL,20,Fby Depp's gesture.                     
